        Property Disclosure Obligations in Queensland: What Sellers Must Tell Buyers
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Queensland's disclosure framework works differently from other states. Understanding what you must disclose, and what you are not required to, protects you and keeps your sale on track.
      </p>
